    public interface PositiveInteger
extends org.apache.xmlbeans.XmlPositiveInteger
    An XML positiveInteger(@http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/). This is an atomic type that is a restriction of org.xmlsoap.schemas.soap.encoding.PositiveInteger.
